This is an APPLICATION for people who want to pretend to be a BOOKSHOP.
It uses an SQLITE database via the SQLALCHEMY package!!


Prerequisites:
>>> python -m pip install fastapi==0.75.0 uvicorn==0.17.6
>>> python -m pip install sqlalchemy==1.4.32
>>> python -m pip install python-dotenv==0.19.2
(>>> python -m pip install validators==0.18.2)

Future updates:
- Add dewey decimal system classification with validators